Here in Lavender Haze we have a giant fish (and Harry's iconic video), mention of the 50s s***(Harry has been seen wearing pearl necklaces - a very common gift choice of the 50s). Also the house theme...we know about Taylor's but surprised when we then have Harry's House.  It pops up so often, wish now I had made a note with each time there was an item or a word or phrase that carried an uncanny similarity or gave me a wiggle in my stomach or heart. A touch of wonder, and reminding. No I'm not supposing any romantic connection, just a mutual respect. But certainly not coincidence. Maybe just a loud "hello, it's Me kind of nod." - and then again maybe nothing at all.
